<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/38202ALTPGKBCKCMLBKRMKDKMNRVJPCCC>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Andrea Menard";
  schema:description """
	An evening of powerful song and storytelling, <span class=\"BoldText\">Andrea Menard</span> in concert is both intimate and inspiring. Blending jazz, blues, and contemporary influences, this performance invites audiences into a space of reflection, connection, and celebration—rooted in culture, resilience, and the strength of voice. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Andrea Menard</span> is an award-winning Métis singer-songwriter and actor known for her lyrical, soulful voice and deeply personal storytelling. With longtime collaborator Robert Walsh, she creates music that bridges cultures and communities. A celebrated performer across Canada, her work uplifts Indigenous voices and honours Métis heritage. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Tickets</span>  <span><br/></span>Premium $50 | Standard $40 | Economy $30 <span><br/></span>New for 26/27: $10 Youth (under 20)<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">The Ultimate Pass</span><span><br/></span>Build your own Darke Hall experience with our <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Ultimate Pass</span></span>!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For $320, choose any 8 Darke Hall Presents performances and reserve your seats at the time of purchase—giving you the flexibility to create a season that fits your interests and schedule while securing your preferred seats early.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Purchase your Ultimate Pass by October 30 and receive complimentary coat check for the entire season as a thank you for supporting Darke Hall early in the season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Every ticket supports the ongoing work of Darke Hall and helps keep this historic stage alive.
""";
