<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/40801ACLMJTSSJPDJLCGJNCRGTMKSPPRR>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Big Band Holiday!";
  schema:description """
	Back by popular demand: the return of <span class=\"BoldText\">Regina Jazz Orchestra’s Big Band Holiday concert!</span><span><br/></span> <span><br/></span>Experience the dazzling re-imagining of the music from <span class=\"BoldText\">“A Charlie Brown Christmas”</span>, infused with timeless charm from the Christmas classic. The evening also features a festive mix of holiday favorites, from toe-tapping classics to soulful seasonal gems. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Performed by a powerhouse ensemble of top-tier musicians, this concert promises joy, nostalgia, and a whole lot of groove. Don’t miss this musical celebration that’ll have you dancing into the holidays!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Tickets are $48.84 for adults and $15.54 for students, inclusive of fees and taxes.  Seating is not assigned.</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>
""";
