<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/37802AKQMQCRDGQHPRGHGDKTDKDVRVDTT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Boy Golden";
  schema:description """
	Laid-back and full of good vibes, <span class=\"BoldText\">Boy Golden</span> brings a night of country-tinged folk with a dreamy, feel-good edge. Rooted in prairie storytelling and easygoing rhythms, this is music that invites you to settle in, slow down, and ride the wave. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Winnipeg artist <span class=\"BoldText\">Liam Duncan</span> performs as Boy Golden, blending country, folk, and psych influences into a warm, lo-fi sound. Emerging in 2020, the project reflects themes of self-discovery and positivity, earning a growing following for its honest songwriting and relaxed, unmistakable style.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Tickets</span>  <span><br/></span>Premium $50 | Standard $40 | Economy $30 <span><br/></span>New for 26/27: $10 Youth (under 20)<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">The Ultimate Pass</span><span><br/></span>Build your own Darke Hall experience with our <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Ultimate Pass</span></span>!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For $320, choose any 8 Darke Hall Presents performances and reserve your seats at the time of purchase—giving you the flexibility to create a season that fits your interests and schedule while securing your preferred seats early.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Purchase your Ultimate Pass by October 30 and receive complimentary coat check for the entire season as a thank you for supporting Darke Hall early in the season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Every ticket supports the ongoing work of Darke Hall and helps keep this historic stage alive.
""";
