<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/36402AQRDJJJGDTRNGGKCMTQHGJQDGGPS>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Burnstick";
  schema:description """
	Intimate, powerful, and deeply moving, <span class=\"BoldText\">Burnstick</span> creates a space for reflection through song. With haunting harmonies and rich instrumentation, their performance invites audiences to slow down, listen closely, and feel the stories woven into every note. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>JUNO-nominated duo <span class=\"BoldText\">Nadia and Jason Burnstick</span> are acclaimed for their cinematic folk sound and emotional storytelling. Based in Manitoba, their music blends striking vocal harmonies with the distinctive tones of the Weissenborn guitar. Their award-winning debut and recent release <span class=\"ItalicText\">Made of Sin</span> have earned national recognition. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Event supported by OSAC</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Tickets</span>  <span><br/></span>Premium $50 | Standard $40 | Economy $30 <span><br/></span>New for 26/27: $10 Youth (under 20)<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">The Ultimate Pass</span><span><br/></span>Build your own Darke Hall experience with our <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Ultimate Pass</span></span>!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For $320, choose any 8 Darke Hall Presents performances and reserve your seats at the time of purchase—giving you the flexibility to create a season that fits your interests and schedule while securing your preferred seats early.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Purchase your Ultimate Pass by October 30 and receive complimentary coat check for the entire season as a thank you for supporting Darke Hall early in the season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Every ticket supports the ongoing work of Darke Hall and helps keep this historic stage alive. 
""";
