<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/39001AMGJLTQNTKSVBHSJCGGLBSSLLVJK>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "CareCon 2026";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"BoldText\">What is The Caring Conference?</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>There’s a particular kind of person who keeps showing up — for their organization, their community, their city. Who measures success not just in revenue, but in impact. Who believes that how you do business says something about who you are.<span><br/></span>CareCon was built for that person.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Now in its second year, CareCon has become one of the most anticipated gatherings for nonprofit and community-minded professionals across the Prairies. CareCon26 is our most ambitious day yet — and we’d love for you to be part of it.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For more information and to register, please visit <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://strategylab.ca/carecon/\">Strategy Lab&#39;s website.</a><span><br/></span>
""";
