<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/36603AMJQVQVRCHKDVVMRBLCHDDBTSRTT>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Celeigh Cardinal – A Very Celeigh Cardinal Christmas";
  schema:description """
	<span class=\"ItalicText\">A Very <span class=\"BoldText\">Celeigh Cardinal</span> Christmas</span> is a heartfelt evening of classic songs, original music, and festive storytelling. With a warm, intimate atmosphere and powerhouse vocals, this show blends nostalgia, soul, and a touch of sparkle into a truly memorable night. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>JUNO Award-winning Métis singer-songwriter <span class=\"BoldText\">Celeigh Cardinal</span> is known for her powerful voice and deeply personal storytelling. A familiar face at Darke Hall, she brings a rich blend of folk, soul, and blues to the stage—creating performances that are both intimate and unforgettable.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Tickets</span>  <span><br/></span>Premium $50 | Standard $40 | Economy $30 <span><br/></span>New for 26/27: $10 Youth (under 20)<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Build Your Own Series</span><span><br/></span>Darke Hall was built for the arts—now you can build your own series. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Pick the shows you love and save when you buy more: <span><br/></span>• 4+ tickets — 10% off <span><br/></span>• 6+ tickets — 15% off <span><br/></span>• 8+ tickets — 20% off <span><br/></span>• 10–12 tickets — 25% off <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Every ticket supports the ongoing work of Darke Hall and helps keep this historic stage alive. 
""";
