<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/36601ATRPSQKSGHPQNCLQHVKLVNDQQCLK>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Dan Mangan: National Light Tour";
  schema:description """
	A master storyteller with a gift for connection, <span class=\"BoldText\">Dan Mangan</span> returns to Darke Hall with an evening of songs that are as thoughtful as they are unforgettable. Blending indie folk with sharp wit and emotional depth, this is a show that feels intimate, honest, and fully alive in the moment. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>A 2x JUNO Award-winning songwriter, <span class=\"BoldText\">Dan Mangan</span> has spent over two decades shaping Canada’s indie folk landscape. Known for his evolving sound and deeply human songwriting, he has built a loyal following through powerful live performances that balance humour, vulnerability, and connection.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Tickets</span>  <span><br/></span>Premium $50 | Standard $40 | Economy $30 <span><br/></span>New for 26/27: $10 Youth (under 20)<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">The Ultimate Pass</span><span><br/></span>Build your own Darke Hall experience with our <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Ultimate Pass</span></span>!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For $320, choose any 8 Darke Hall Presents performances and reserve your seats at the time of purchase—giving you the flexibility to create a season that fits your interests and schedule while securing your preferred seats early.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Purchase your Ultimate Pass by October 30 and receive complimentary coat check for the entire season as a thank you for supporting Darke Hall early in the season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Every ticket helps keep this stage alive with music, stories, and shared moments. 
""";
