  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Deck the Hall Holiday Sing-Along";
  schema:description """
	Sing it loud. Sing it together. Deck the (Darke) Hall is a joyful holiday sing-along filled with classic carols and community spirit. Bring your friends, family, and festive energy as we gather in the hall for an afternoon of music, laughter, and shared celebration. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Featuring <span class=\"BoldText\">The Tuesdays</span>, this community-driven afternoon puts the spotlight on local voices. Known for their warmth and enthusiasm, the group leads the room in song—creating a welcoming, all-ages experience where everyone is part of the performance. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Tickets</span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Pay What You Will</span>
""";
