  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "God Is A Scottish Drag Queen";
  schema:description """
	Part comedy, part commentary, and entirely unforgettable—<span class=\"BoldText\">God Is A Scottish Drag Queen</span> sees the Almighty return to Earth with a lot to say. Expect sharp wit, big laughs, and a surprisingly thoughtful take on humanity, pop culture, and everything in between. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Created and performed by Canadian comedian <span class=\"BoldText\">Mike Delamont</span>, this award-winning one-man show has become an international hit. Blending stand-up, theatre, and character comedy, <span class=\"BoldText\">Delamont</span> delivers a bold and brilliant performance that’s equal parts hilarious and insightful.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Tickets</span>  <span><br/></span>Premium $50 | Standard $40 | Economy $30 <span><br/></span>New for 26/27: $10 Youth (under 20)<span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Please note that this performance is recommended for ages 16 and up, due to coarse language and adult content.</span></span><span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">The Ultimate Pass</span><span><br/></span>Build your own Darke Hall experience with our <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Ultimate Pass</span></span>!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For $320, choose any 8 Darke Hall Presents performances and reserve your seats at the time of purchase—giving you the flexibility to create a season that fits your interests and schedule while securing your preferred seats early.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Purchase your Ultimate Pass by October 30 and receive complimentary coat check for the entire season as a thank you for supporting Darke Hall early in the season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This historic hall stays vibrant because people like you show up. 
""";
