  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Hawksley Workman";
  schema:description """
	Bold, theatrical, and endlessly inventive, <span class=\"BoldText\">Hawksley Workman</span> brings a genre-bending night of pop, rock, and cabaret to the stage. With dynamic musicianship and a flair for the unexpected, this is a performance that moves from intimate moments to full, electric spectacle. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"BoldText\">Hawksley Workman</span> is a critically acclaimed Canadian singer-songwriter and multi-instrumentalist. With over a decade-spanning career and eleven albums, he’s known for his prolific creativity and distinctive sound. Whether on guitar, piano, or drums, his live performances are as versatile as they are unforgettable. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Tickets</span>  <span><br/></span>Premium $50 | Standard $40 | Economy $30 <span><br/></span>New for 26/27: $10 Youth (under 20)<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">The Ultimate Pass</span><span><br/></span>Build your own Darke Hall experience with our <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Ultimate Pass</span></span>!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For $320, choose any 8 Darke Hall Presents performances and reserve your seats at the time of purchase—giving you the flexibility to create a season that fits your interests and schedule while securing your preferred seats early.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Purchase your Ultimate Pass by October 30 and receive complimentary coat check for the entire season as a thank you for supporting Darke Hall early in the season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Every ticket supports the artists and the experiences that bring us together. 
""";
