  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Jill Barber – A Holly Jolly Christmas";
  schema:description """
	Step into the warmth of the season with <span class=\"BoldText\">Jill Barber’s</span> <span class=\"ItalicText\">Holly Jolly Christmas</span> show. Blending holiday classics with her signature charm, this intimate and elegant performance is filled with storytelling, nostalgia, and just the right amount of sparkle—perfect for a cozy night out. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>3-time JUNO Award nominee <span class=\"BoldText\">Jill Barber</span> is celebrated for her timeless voice and genre-spanning style. Her 2025 holiday album was met with sold-out shows across Canada, showcasing her gift for connection and storytelling. Joined by an exceptional band, she brings a refined and heartfelt take to holiday music. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Tickets</span>  <span><br/></span>Premium $50 | Standard $40 | Economy $30 <span><br/></span>New for 26/27: $10 Youth (under 20)<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">The Ultimate Pass</span><span><br/></span>Build your own Darke Hall experience with our <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Ultimate Pass</span></span>!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For $320, choose any 8 Darke Hall Presents performances and reserve your seats at the time of purchase—giving you the flexibility to create a season that fits your interests and schedule while securing your preferred seats early.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Purchase your Ultimate Pass by October 30 and receive complimentary coat check for the entire season as a thank you for supporting Darke Hall early in the season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Every ticket helps us keep creating moments that matter. 
