<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/37201ANNHRQCTNHTBVHBGGJGJCBQDGBJG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "JJ Voss – Tribute to Steve Earle’s Guitar Town";
  schema:description """
	Marking the 40th anniversary of <span class=\"ItalicText\">Guitar Town</span>, <span class=\"BoldText\">JJ Voss</span> pays tribute to Steve Earle with a night of roots-driven storytelling and classic Americana. Honest, heartfelt, and full of grit, this show celebrates the songs that defined a generation—brought to life with a local voice. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Raised on a farm in southern Saskatchewan, <span class=\"BoldText\">JJ Voss</span> is a seasoned singer-songwriter with nearly two decades of performing and recording. Influenced by artists like Steve Earle, Tom Petty, and Bruce Springsteen, his music is rooted in lived experience—authentic, hardworking, and deeply connected to place. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Tickets</span>  <span><br/></span>Premium $50 | Standard $40 | Economy $30 <span><br/></span>New for 26/27: $10 Youth (under 20)<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">The Ultimate Pass</span><span><br/></span>Build your own Darke Hall experience with our <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Ultimate Pass</span></span>!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For $320, choose any 8 Darke Hall Presents performances and reserve your seats at the time of purchase—giving you the flexibility to create a season that fits your interests and schedule while securing your preferred seats early.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Purchase your Ultimate Pass by October 30 and receive complimentary coat check for the entire season as a thank you for supporting Darke Hall early in the season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Your ticket helps make space for artists, audiences, and community to connect. 
""";
