<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/40601AVRVRQNNTTMJRHQKDLRCKSKHBGKP>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "On the Big Screen";
  schema:description """
	Step into the spotlight with the <span class=\"BoldText\">2026 Living Skies Irish Dance Recital: On the Big Screen.</span> <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This year's recital is an unforgettable celebration of music, movement, and movie magic!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join Living Skies Irish Dance as our dancers bring beloved songs from iconic movies, television shows, and stage productions to life through the energy and artistry of Irish dance. From heart-pounding rhythms to cinematic storytelling, this year’s recital promises an evening filled with sparkle, passion, and standing ovation moments worthy of the silver screen.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Lights. Music. Hard shoes. Action. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Tickets are $23.10 inclusive of fees and taxes.  Seating is assigned.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>All sales are final; no refunds issued.</span><span><br/></span>
""";
