<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/42001AQJJQTSKLLKMRKNHHDRNVHRLPNPB>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Regina Musical Club - Ménestrel";
  schema:description """
	Savour the tradition of the troubadours, as <span class=\"BoldText\">Ménestrel</span> breathes vivid life into music that has been shaped by centuries. Their voyage through historic repertoire is accented by <span class=\"BoldText\">lute, guitar, recorder, and the intricate colours of the human voice</span>. With selections ranging from grand compositions by Purcell, Dowland, and Monteverdi to nostalgic Gaelic, Québécois, and English folk melodies, Ménestrel reminds us of the pleasure of these musical forms.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>The group consists of recognized artists <span class=\"BoldText\">Janelle Lucyk (soprano), Kerry Bursey (tenor, guitar and lute) and Vincent Lauzer (recorder)</span>, who have established a reputation for combining ancient repertoire with elements of folk song. Ménestrel has performed across Canada and in Europe, including a “Messiah-on-the-go!” production featuring emerging performers in historic Nova Scotian venues.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Join us for a refreshing portrayal of song and story that feels as approachable and inviting today as it did centuries ago.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Tickets</span>  <span><br/></span>Advance $35 | Door $40 <span><br/></span>U of R Students & Under 18 Free (only available at the door)<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Full Season Subscription & 3 Pack Passes</span><span><br/></span>Support the Regina Musical Club and save by purchasing a 6 concert full season subscription for $180 or a 3 Pack for $97.50!<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">All prices are inclusive of fees and taxes.</span>
""";
  schema:startDate "2027-02-07T15:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
