<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/36401AGDPLVGNCJMRKTPQLBSBLCVKVSMG>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "SKERRYVORE";
  schema:description """
	High-energy and impossible to sit still, <span class=\"BoldText\">SKERRYVORE</span> bring a full-throttle Celtic rock party to Darke Hall. Blending traditional Scottish roots with modern influences, this is a night of big sound, driving rhythms, and feel-good energy that turns the room into a celebration. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Formed in Scotland, <span class=\"BoldText\">SKERRYVORE</span> has grown from local ceilidh roots into an internationally celebrated band. With six studio albums and global tours across Europe, North America, and beyond, their sound fuses Celtic tradition with rock, pop, and more—creating a dynamic, genre-crossing live experience. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Tickets</span>  <span><br/></span>Premium $50 | Standard $40 | Economy $30 <span><br/></span>New for 26/27: $10 Youth (under 20)<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">The Ultimate Pass</span><span><br/></span>Build your own Darke Hall experience with our <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Ultimate Pass</span></span>!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For $320, choose any 8 Darke Hall Presents performances and reserve your seats at the time of purchase—giving you the flexibility to create a season that fits your interests and schedule while securing your preferred seats early.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Purchase your Ultimate Pass by October 30 and receive complimentary coat check for the entire season as a thank you for supporting Darke Hall early in the season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Every ticket supports the ongoing work of Darke Hall and helps keep the lights on our historic stage.
""";
