<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/38401ANGTJSBMBHBQLHQPNRBLQSPPBRDN>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Arrogant Worms";
  schema:description """
	Silly, smart, and completely unpredictable, <span class=\"BoldText\">The Arrogant Worms</span> bring a night of musical comedy that doesn’t take itself too seriously. Expect absurd lyrics, catchy tunes, and plenty of laughs—including a few songs you’ll be singing long after you leave. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Formed in 1991, <span class=\"BoldText\">The Arrogant Worms</span> are one of Canada’s most beloved musical comedy acts. With over 30 years of touring and 13 albums, their satirical songs have built a loyal following—featuring cult favourites like “The Last Saskatchewan Pirate.” <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Tickets</span>  <span><br/></span>Premium $50 | Standard $40 | Economy $30 <span><br/></span>New for 26/27: $10 Youth (under 20)<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">The Ultimate Pass</span><span><br/></span>Build your own Darke Hall experience with our <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Ultimate Pass</span></span>!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For $320, choose any 8 Darke Hall Presents performances and reserve your seats at the time of purchase—giving you the flexibility to create a season that fits your interests and schedule while securing your preferred seats early.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Purchase your Ultimate Pass by October 30 and receive complimentary coat check for the entire season as a thank you for supporting Darke Hall early in the season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Every ticket is part of something bigger than a single night.
""";
