<http://www.spektrix.com/darkehallsociety/event/38601APMJBSGHLBVKJDHHGBQTTKBBSMSJ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Johner Brothers";
  schema:description """
	A prairie favourite returns. <span class=\"BoldText\">The Johner Brothers</span> bring their signature country sound back to the stage for a night of hits, harmony, and high-energy performance. Blending nostalgia with fresh energy, this is a show that celebrates a legendary career—and the joy of live music. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>CCMA award winners and Canadian country icons, <span class=\"BoldText\">The Johner Brothers</span> built a legacy with chart-topping albums and unforgettable live shows. Now reunited after two decades, Brad and Ken return with a new generation on stage—delivering the sound and spirit fans know and love. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"ItalicText\">Event supported by OSAC</span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">Tickets</span>  <span><br/></span>Premium $50 | Standard $40 | Economy $30 <span><br/></span>New for 26/27: $10 Youth (under 20)<span><br/></span> <span><br/></span><span class=\"UnderlineText\">The Ultimate Pass</span><span><br/></span>Build your own Darke Hall experience with our <span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">Ultimate Pass</span></span>!<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>For $320, choose any 8 Darke Hall Presents performances and reserve your seats at the time of purchase—giving you the flexibility to create a season that fits your interests and schedule while securing your preferred seats early.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Purchase your Ultimate Pass by October 30 and receive complimentary coat check for the entire season as a thank you for supporting Darke Hall early in the season.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>This historic hall stays vibrant because people like you show up.<span><br/></span>
""";
